            "sample": [
              "smatch (`viewer/src/RemotionPreview.tsx`, `viewer/src/App.tsx`, `viewer/src/OverlayEditor.tsx`)",
              "**Scope:** Small \u2014 single constant change + prop threading",
              "",
              "The root cause: `RemotionPreview.tsx:12` sets `PREVIEW_SCALE = 0.5`, making the Remotion composition 640x360. Clip coordinates in `timeline.json` are in canonical 1280x720 space. `VisualClip.tsx` applies `left: clip.x` directly in the reduced composition space, placing the clip at the wrong position. The overlay uses 1280 for its projection, creating a second mismatch."
            ]
          },
