              "\"robustness\": \"standard\",",
              "  \"signals\": {",
              "    \"iteration\": 3,",
              "    \"idea\": \"Build on Remotion Studio (npx remotion studio) as the foundation. Phase 1: Replace the ffmpeg render pipeline with Remotion compositions that read a shared JSON config (timeline.json + asset-registry.json). Use Remotion Studio for preview/playback. Control the timeline via natural language (Claude editing the JSON config) and Python tools (view.py, place.py, ingest.py, etc). Phase 2 (later): Layer on visual editing tools (drag-drop timeline, canvas editing, property inspector) on top. KEY CONSTRAINTS: 1) Two edit paths writing to same config: AI agent (natural language) and eventually visual UI. 2) Config must be JSON - easy for both AI and tools to read/write. 3) Remotion is the render engine - reads config, produces video. 4) Python tools continue to work - they write to shared asset registry. 5) Start simple with Remotion Studio + natural language editing, add visual editing UI later. 6) Project is open source.\","
            ]
          },
